information: The company MAGNA APIS S.L, is a Manufacturer/ Producer, founded in 2010, which operates in the Fruit preserves and jams industry. It is based in Los Corrales De Buelna, Spain.
products: Miel, Polen, Hidromiel, Mermeladas artesanas. | Miel con nueces | Mermelada de Fresas | Mermelada de Mango | Mermelada de Arándanos | Mermelada de Pimientos Asados | Mermelada de Mandarinas | Mermelada de Higos | Mermeladas SIN azúcar añadido
